<div class="markdown"><h1 id="Composite-UMAP">Composite UMAP</h1><p>Combining multiple 'views' of the same dataset into a single projection.</p></div>


<div class="markdown"><p>As a simple example, we can split the Fashion MNIST dataset in two: one with the top half of the images and the other with the bottom half.</p></div>
